originalText.text: Kat helped my partner and I find and apartment, and I cannot speak more highly of her. Kat was super responsive throughout our search, which was invaluable - even answering our text messages late on the weekends! She made the experience a lot easier than it would have been, had we tried to do find a property ourselves. I couldn’t recommend her more !

originalText.text: Katerina was really great in helping us find an apartment! As internationals, we were new to the process and she expertly guided us through all the stages. We gained a successful application after just 2 weeks of being in the city. Would highly recommend!

originalText.text: I have only good things to say about WJFNY Real Estate. Their professionalism, timeliness, and determination to deliver impeccable service is like no other I have encountered in NYC. Suzanne assisted us from viewing, to signing and all the way to delivery of our new home. With meticulous vetting, and attentive communication, I am pleased to say we were taken care of throughout the ever stressful process of finding our new home. New adventures await us and it's thanks to our friends at WJFNY Real Estate. Massive thank you to Suzanne and team. To those looking for help, know you're in good hands.

originalText.text:
Our experience has been nothing short of exceptional! WJFNY’s dedication and support made finding our new place stress-free. Bill warmly introduced us to a stunning building, while Suzanne expertly navigated us through the everything else including the entire application process - she has been extremely helpful every step of the way. Suzanne’s responsiveness and friendliness made her great to work with and we were always kept in the loop with updates. I can honestly say their 'treating clients like family' slogan is more than just a motto, it's their authentic way of service that I felt from my first inquiry all the way to receiving our keys!

Having just moved to New York a couple of months ago, I was also concerned about the application process as foreigner on a working visa, however their expertise and guidance made the whole process so simple and seamless.

If you're seeking a rental experience filled with genuine care, efficiency and professionalism, I wholeheartedly recommend WJFNY. Suzanne and Bill, thank you so much for all your support as we start a new and exciting chapter in a beautiful New York apartment!
